headline: Micron Earnings, More Powell Testimony, Inflation Data: Still to Come This Week
summary: It's day two of Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell's testimony before Congress. The Fed’s preferred inflation gauge is due later in the week, as are earnings from Nike. Results from memory-chip maker Micron are due Wednesday.
